{"EpubVersion":2,"filepath":"","fixparentnode":"","floatingtheme":[],"folded":false,"markups":[{"date":"2025-03-11 21:56:00","docid":0,"id":3,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"胡嘉在“自序”中强调越南和中国在文化上的相似性。这几乎是当时中国人越南游记中的共性。","page":11,"rect":[8.999999731779099,11.399999660253542,333.99999007582693,52.59999846220021],"type":11,"uuid":"9b165d46380b26b8c4eec0249a45c98e"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:00:37","docid":0,"id":4,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"作者在“自序”中说明其赴云南和越南的机缘在于1937年9月26日，胡嘉从北平出发南归，因为时局和交通问题而辗转到上述两地。","page":10,"rect":[13.799999588727928,5.399999839067476,327.9999902546408,57.99999830126767],"type":11,"uuid":"f845bc7a856ff1fb425a08cc6cfc2353"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:19:12","docid":0,"id":5,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"第70页中，胡嘉认为苗夷和乡巴佬没有什么区别。（汉族中心主义的思考方式）","page":81,"rect":[20.39999939203267,11.399999660253542,308.1999908447268,57.99999830126768],"type":11,"uuid":"75ed7a2fde0b620b2d6aac4206526635"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:20:08","docid":0,"id":6,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"胡嘉认为蒙自的苗夷像外国人一样。","page":82,"rect":[59.399998229742096,16.79999949932099,294.99999123811745,44.799998694658306],"type":11,"uuid":"8377b0636c547dcc2f9f606e6afdaa2d"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:22:10","docid":0,"id":8,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"胡嘉在这里又认为中华民族是整个的，这跟前面将苗夷看成“乡巴佬”、“外国人”的心态有所差异。","page":85,"rect":[15.599999535083839,13.199999606609353,317.1999905765059,69.99999794363981],"type":11,"uuid":"48ac6220fbb495af3688f68d58526a8b"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:25:37","docid":0,"id":10,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"滇越铁路的另一层意义在于沟通了云南与中国内地的联系，从云南三天三夜就可以到海防，再乘坐两天的轮船就可以到香港，最多一周到上海。","page":88,"rect":[10.199999696016334,6.599999803304684,326.199990308285,56.199998354911855],"type":11,"uuid":"0d2dc8e74b3a7966d2ab17db069501db"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:27:42","docid":0,"id":11,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"滇越铁路是一条拼命筑成的铁路，大量的中国工人因此而殒命。","page":87,"rect":[56.39999831914906,20.39999939203264,295.59999122023606,66.99999803304678],"type":11,"uuid":"f480e683a0f7312f042e4fa1d883818c"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:29:28","docid":0,"id":12,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"滇越铁路同时也是一条没有主权的大动脉。法国希望通过这条铁路扩张其在云南乃至中国西南的影响力，同时遏制英国势力的增长。","page":89,"rect":[7.799999767541863,8.999999731779099,329.199990218878,58.59999828338627],"type":11,"uuid":"96f55df4a0463eae010f35fcfe3b859c"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:31:25","docid":0,"id":14,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"从嘉林的越南文写法\"Gia Lam \"来看，胡嘉似乎懂得一些越南语。","page":90,"rect":[19.799999409913994,488.99998542666475,329.7999902009966,527.1999843180184],"type":11,"uuid":"2cfd78279f80ff0628e24c61148e31a8"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:32:05","docid":0,"id":15,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"坐滇越铁路带给人一种“老牛破车”的体验。","page":90,"rect":[31.799999052286125,25.1999992489815,301.5999910414221,55.59999837279322],"type":11,"uuid":"aab39c1fe5da8272f6c8a2de43796a46"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:34:48","docid":0,"id":18,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"从第79页的内容来看，胡嘉并非首次来越南，他此前也曾经坐滇越铁路从海防到昆明。","page":91,"rect":[28.499999150633812,9.749999709427357,249.99999257922192,62.49999816715722],"type":11,"uuid":"f7b7448bd1fe32b416c2553b95e7cd46"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:36:39","docid":0,"id":19,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"滇越铁路之所以是破车。1、速度很慢；2、沿途停驶，乘客需要自行下车并且寻找住宿的地方，沿途上上下下很不方便，因为滇越铁路不开客运夜车。","page":90,"rect":[2.999999910593033,151.4999954849483,48.99999856948857,534.9999840855603],"type":11,"uuid":"acdbd9037d9dce5be1047a9783cd418b"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:40:58","docid":0,"id":20,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"云南境内的一些越南人已经归化为中国人。他们自认为中国人，但是服饰和风俗依然保留了一部分越南的特色。（这个风俗指的是牙齿染成漆黑）。作者认为他们没有中国人的风度，对此抱持批评的看法。","page":92,"rect":[0,1.4999999552965164,342.24998982995777,70.74999792128807],"type":11,"uuid":"334be63bfba8cbee3c8894f186c240d5"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:42:25","docid":0,"id":22,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"胡嘉对于已经归化中国的越南人的批评，反映了抗战之际中国知识界对于族群多样性的担忧。","page":92,"rect":[3.749999888241291,487.4999854713683,333.99999007582693,527.4999843090777],"type":11,"uuid":"5d2fd34bb6589450b577fb8027d4bb29"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:47:34","docid":0,"id":24,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"滇越铁路之特色为众多的山洞和铁桥。","page":94,"rect":[41.2499987706542,23.999999284744263,303.2499909922483,57.249998323619394],"type":11,"uuid":"f7e60518065546fc5c348fbf8c7920b2"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:51:41","docid":0,"id":25,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"胡嘉在《滇越游记》中对于滇越铁路的描述，不管是乘坐体验，还是沿途概括，以及更为详细的票价等信息，都有说明。","page":98,"rect":[15.749999530613422,14.999999552965164,320.4999904781583,67.74999801069502],"type":11,"uuid":"6d35f932dfe0e654251d1d2a54b94c35"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:54:38","docid":0,"id":26,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"海防到香港、上海、河内、昆明、西贡等地相对都比较方便。当时很多国人如果到云南，更愿意从海防到昆明，而非从内地走陆路到云南。","page":100,"rect":[17.999999463558197,6.749999798834324,318.2499905452135,74.49999780952938],"type":11,"uuid":"4b39348cfb2a48b8a0f1b2c613a30a0f"},{"date":"2025-03-11 23:04:58","docid":0,"id":27,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"海防人口约5万，其中华侨占据1/10.","page":101,"rect":[116.24999653548014,15.749999530613422,337.7499899640682,36.99999892711641],"type":11,"uuid":"e32b86f21df53eaaad1b8a2a3b7903b9"},{"date":"2025-03-11 23:06:49","docid":0,"id":28,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"旅越华侨富于国家观念。虽然环境有所限制，但是他们依然在努力做对国家有利之事。","page":101,"rect":[13.499999597668648,488.9999854266648,339.24998991936474,531.249984197319],"type":11,"uuid":"195ad735f54809820623da95ee1d9f4e"},{"date":"2025-03-11 23:07:49","docid":0,"id":29,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"海防华侨的分布区域。","page":102,"rect":[112.49999664723885,38.2499988600612,252.99999248981499,59.49999825656418],"type":11,"uuid":"4dc4e4a9a90021d2e3167152350c12ea"},{"date":"2025-03-11 23:08:19","docid":0,"id":30,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"胡嘉在第91页也提到了“天然旅馆”。与此同时，还有新亚旅馆也很著名。","page":102,"rect":[8.24999975413084,480.74998567253397,318.2499905452135,531.249984197319],"type":11,"uuid":"502cd86e716dac0d7ce192a490b69f8d"},{"date":"2025-03-11 23:09:26","docid":0,"id":31,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"抗战爆发以后，海防华侨自发停止销售日货。","page":103,"rect":[115.49999655783188,494.2499852702026,336.99998998641996,531.249984197319],"type":11,"uuid":"c88e9799157a851985d0f8c2b0015d41"},{"date":"2025-03-11 23:10:46","docid":0,"id":32,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"海防和华侨相关的宗教建筑：天后宫、财神殿、送子观音殿。","page":103,"rect":[32.99999901652336,11.249999664723873,310.74999076873087,46.74999863654378],"type":11,"uuid":"be2acc0827049090e51ea560ac3e523c"},{"date":"2025-03-11 23:12:12","docid":0,"id":33,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"胡嘉说这时越南没有华字日报，或许是记忆错误。","page":103,"rect":[0,117.74999649077665,49.749998547136826,282.9999915957453],"type":11,"uuid":"1db24e65c228d14f4666656cfef5cf93"},{"date":"2025-03-11 23:13:11","docid":0,"id":35,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"海防华侨中学校","page":104,"rect":[257.99999231100105,198.7499940767886,290.49999137222795,370.74998898059164],"type":11,"uuid":"99f64f67e8782376610502264449b5ed"},{"date":"2025-03-11 23:14:07","docid":0,"id":36,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"谭植三先生为华侨教育做出贡献。","page":104,"rect":[116.24999653548014,485.9999855160718,324.2499903663996,507.24998491257475],"type":11,"uuid":"19eef50aa156307f811524ce79aa948b"},{"date":"2025-03-11 23:15:18","docid":0,"id":37,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"当地华侨学校并没有法文和越南文课程，说明它跟当地社会很大程度上是脱节的，是典型的位于越南的中国人学校。","page":104,"rect":[0,98.249997071922,39.99999883770946,459.24998634308616],"type":11,"uuid":"f7934e53bfd3dd1eb3e7800ac92e5487"},{"date":"2025-03-11 23:19:23","docid":0,"id":38,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"第94页，作者在安南皇帝避暑处和越南人合影，后者则被自己的朋友揶揄，说是像一块黑树根。（这是游记中所记载的胡嘉与越南本地人互动的场景，但是后者的形象却较为负面）。","page":105,"rect":[2.999999910593033,7.499999776482582,336.99998998641996,71.49999789893633],"type":11,"uuid":"24e0aa66f4876294c1fa8bf3ececadc2"},{"date":"2025-03-11 23:21:46","docid":0,"id":40,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"胡嘉在海防带有赌博性质的露天游艺场玩乐之经验。","page":106,"rect":[17.999999463558197,3.749999888241291,198.99999409914034,40.74999881535771],"type":11,"uuid":"bde6ab5572d17071b0d89ce73135e3ee"}],"maxid":42,"notelinks":[],"summaries":[],"title":"胡嘉 1939年 - 滇越游记","unimportant":[{"date":"2025-03-11 21:54:41","docid":0,"id":1,"imgfile":"6af5beff1ef1fe67cbbf7386f0dc55d4.png","linecolor":"ffff0000","linestyle":1,"linewidth":3,"page":11,"rect":[175.79999476075187,82.19999755024917,179.39999465346352,493.199985301495,148.19999558329593,59.99999821186071,153.5999954223634,454.79998644590415,127.1999962091447,64.79999806880956,133.19999603033077,407.3999878585342],"type":1,"uuid":"4ec042e6906627efb86a5bc930dce2b1"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:21:27","docid":0,"id":7,"imgfile":"884ab51aca1a26e6913b8578d4046617.png","linecolor":"ffff0000","linestyle":1,"linewidth":3,"page":85,"rect":[53.39999840855603,95.39999715685852,52.199998444318815,485.3999855339531],"type":1,"uuid":"d25e094ab9287232e7586b97e13ef6c3"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:30:43","docid":0,"id":13,"imgfile":"56b751f8d3bdc87c6214d34a9e0bbd4c.png","linecolor":"ffff0000","linestyle":1,"linewidth":3,"page":90,"rect":[171.59999488592163,396.59998818039924,172.79999485015884,484.1999855697159],"type":1,"uuid":"1623b940469e8d9e2074856f6864534b"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:33:48","docid":0,"id":16,"imgfile":"c57e236baf2fd1a79a47f8ddf0dd9af6.png","linecolor":"ffff0000","linestyle":1,"linewidth":3,"page":90,"rect":[142.19999576210986,85.1999974608422,140.99999579787266,464.9999861419205,117.59999649524698,70.19999790787702,121.19999638795862,391.7999883234504],"type":1,"uuid":"0e430e59cd061de02a781dcad6a9bda0"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:34:00","docid":0,"id":17,"imgfile":"dadccd37d0bae114c54e5c84e57c2615.png","linecolor":"ffff0000","linestyle":1,"linewidth":3,"page":90,"rect":[120.74999640136969,425.99998730421106,121.49999637901794,457.4999863654379,95.24999716132888,71.99999785423284,98.24999707192191,459.7499862983827],"type":1,"uuid":"c6a6838309bf0bacd265997addde5b17"},{"date":"2025-03-11 22:47:13","docid":0,"id":23,"imgfile":"5b443d92c6c7da99b0e488bdd66c7171.png","linecolor":"ffff0000","linestyle":1,"linewidth":3,"page":94,"rect":[264.7499921098354,93.74999720603236,266.99999204278015,308.2499908134344],"type":1,"uuid":"a3c943c32286e77ca2db7e067b9c4ccc"},{"date":"2025-03-11 23:12:59","docid":0,"id":34,"imgfile":"86f702c4aec241be8ce641806bc34f2d.png","linecolor":"ffff0000","linestyle":1,"linewidth":3,"page":104,"rect":[258.7499922886493,110.99999669194231,260.9999922215941,191.99999427795427],"type":1,"uuid":"d6572e4bcdb1e6ae4c9db93942108477"},{"date":"2025-03-11 23:21:34","docid":0,"id":39,"imgfile":"39da1930bccd01634b4f139ecb2702a6.png","linecolor":"ffff0000","linestyle":1,"linewidth":3,"page":105,"rect":[206.99999383091944,257.99999231100105,208.49999378621598,313.4999906569722],"type":1,"uuid":"caa7a815a6d23afeaee9b533bc649a2e"},{"date":"2025-03-11 23:23:29","docid":0,"id":41,"imgfile":"582e3a249fedd35dd6aeba854336cadc.png","linecolor":"ffff0000","linestyle":1,"linewidth":3,"page":106,"rect":[111.74999666959057,229.4999931603672,114.7499965801836,300.7499910369518],"type":1,"uuid":"63da4f429407783ef2a0b49a1976d444"}]}